title: #91: Good Fatitude
itunes:title: Good Fatitude with Jamie Caparulo
description: Jamie Caparulo brought me some crazy Japanese ice cream cookies and we talked about how she's going to let herself get fat. She's married now and she's made a decision to let it all go to waste. I don't think I've heard anyone properly express how little marriage makes you care about your looks.
